{"tid":1590122,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［抹黑示威者] 拒絕藍店，勿食旺角新開小食店 ＂八公＂","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T05:52:21.000Z","uid":2076,"like":90,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"00368dab43175f1659ad7aaf579148eabf638b68","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n見行過新開諗住幫襯，一行埋去已經聽到老闆話每月要交19萬租，企多陣聽到相中著紅色曼聯波衫嘅老闆忙住巴結班大陸遊客：<br />\n<br />\n老闆對住班大陸遊客話：你地多d黎幫襯，拿，我俾張vip8折你地，唉，我地好惨呀捱貴租，出面又笠笠亂，你地知唔知沈日有個女仔拎野打個阿伯呀，唉...幾離譜...我俾相你地睇呀...<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度...好彩未叫野食未俾錢即刻擰轉身離開，以後唔好叫香港人幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZLV9kU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZLV9kU.jpg&h=48a95537&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NbinFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NbinFV.jpg&h=23bfed3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#深藍<br />\n#八公<br />\n#旺角<br />\n#極不推介<br />\n#勿嘥錢<br />\n<br />\n原post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2701324926545942&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=df2af16a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942</a><br />\n<br />\n本身放工經過見到新開，諗住下次試下<br />\n點知碌下facebook見到個咁嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻打消念頭<br />\n個舖19萬嫁，好撚貴嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交唔到租，蝕入肉就冇得食嫁啦<br />\n啲支那狗快啲食多啲啊，老細維唔到皮就仆街嫁啦"},{"pid":"021fab0ca661f9445c5abd607f05efa69751749e","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6107d29b10e62c4bd03fd53843e374d68f2acdc","tid":1590122,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"cd7e20a8d3d47c83faa2c89ae25d1159f80fbb5a","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:44:39.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e15508b9bb9c75769bfcc2a7ea80a6f1a773a7e","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710453525063a66b6696ff46831410d9a2c849a3","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5c7a6c9e88965b415a2f9f28b023948d09b8a2","tid":1590122,"uid":12244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"咪撚食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67660287fd52726c28ea0889a8902e3276f5398","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff95d542e8ef9265931b467a78501854b924b9a","tid":1590122,"uid":211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c70096474b735ffd4a6d76b84d7e1725d6340142","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2dcc2f5c0fdda3948117b4f251ecfc3a7124fa2","tid":1590122,"uid