ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f323bee7cabfbd55d22904b2a092e2be1c6f89","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T23:35:49.000Z","msg":"再次提下大家"},{"pid":"74af67f2164273ff4675bc0e78ded19165c43ec3","tid":1590122,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00368dab43175f1659ad7aaf579148eabf638b68","tid":1590122,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n見行過新開諗住幫襯，一行埋去已經聽到老闆話每月要交19萬租，企多陣聽到相中著紅色曼聯波衫嘅老闆忙住巴結班大陸遊客：<br />\n<br />\n老闆對住班大陸遊客話：你地多d黎幫襯，拿，我俾張vip8折你地，唉，我地好惨呀捱貴租，出面又笠笠亂，你地知唔知沈日有個女仔拎野打個阿伯呀，唉...幾離譜...我俾相你地睇呀...<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度...好彩未叫野食未俾錢即刻擰轉身離開，以後唔好叫香港人幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZLV9kU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZLV9kU.jpg&h=48a95537&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NbinFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NbinFV.jpg&h=23bfed3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#深藍<br />\n#八公<br />\n#旺角<br />\n#極不推介<br />\n#勿嘥錢<br />\n<br />\n原post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2701324926545942&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=df2af16a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942</a><br />\n<br />\n本身放工經過見到新開，諗住下次試下<br />\n點知碌下facebook見到個咁嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻打消念頭<br />\n個舖19萬嫁，好撚貴嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交唔到租，蝕入肉就冇得食嫁啦<br />\n啲支那狗快啲食多啲啊，老細維唔到皮就仆街嫁啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T00:37:47.000Z","msg":"食佢d嘢疴死你！"},{"pid":"fd69f29152af8e58354014c867eb03a5785b0778","tid":1590122,"uid":171849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09